@ description: Weekend triathlon brick session
@ author: Coach Rivera
@ tags: triathlon, race prep, olympic distance

# Swim [Open Water Swimming] (2026-03-15 07:00)
@ location: Lake Zurich

> Practice sighting every 6 strokes. Total: 1800m.

- Swim 400m @Z1
- 4x:
  - Swim 200m @Z3
  - Recover 100m @Z1
- Swim 200m @Z1

# Bike [Cycling] (2026-03-15 08:00-09:00)
@ location: Zurich — Rapperswil loop

> Aim for 33-34 km/h average on the flat section.

- Warmup 10min @Z1
- Bike 30min @85% FTP
- 3x:
  - Bike 3min @95% FTP
  - Recover 2min @Z1
- Cooldown 10min @Z1

# Brick Run [Running] (2026-03-15 09:00)

> Legs will feel heavy — push through the first km.
> Transition practice: bike-to-run in under 90s.

- Run 3km @5:00/km
- Run 2km @4:30/km
- Cooldown 1km @Z1
